These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, nigerian, turkish
1. the turkish is on the left of the nigerian##1
2. the turkish is between the russian and the nigerian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | russian | turkish | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, western, crime
1. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching western movies and the person watching crime movies##2
2. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | thriller | western |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, disco, trance
1. the fan of disco is between the fan of punk and the fan of trance##2
2. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | trance | disco | punk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: dog, frog, cat
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the dog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | dog | cat | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, tea
1. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking soy-milk##2
2. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee | tea |

 #################################

 
